node.text: Probably going to get copyright for this one but till it happens- here it is. Me and toot’s final ride in the Twinkie for season two. What a fucking journey it’s been. Hope you guys enjoy. Here’s us, doing what JJ & JB do best. Break things. Love you guys. P4L

node.text: Well today’s the day. Season 2 is yours. Hope you guys are enjoying it and hopefully have gotten a little bit of sleep. Love you all and thanks so much for supporting our little show. You guys rock. P4L babayyy ALSO! Whoever left me this message in the Twinkie that day, that was super fun to find. Made me smile :)

node.text: Probably going to get copyright for this one but till it happens- here it is. Me and toot’s final ride in the Twinkie for season two. What a fucking journey it’s been. Hope you guys enjoy. Here’s us, doing what JJ & JB do best. Break things. Love you guys. P4L
